WEBVTT

00:02.529 --> 00:03.580
We're doomed.

00:03.729 --> 00:05.759
- We can make a break for it.
- Impossible.

00:06.129 --> 00:08.300
- Front exit?
- We'd be spotted instantly.

00:09.130 --> 00:10.460
Back door?

00:11.529 --> 00:13.419
- Blocked.
- That's it, then.

00:13.929 --> 00:16.739
- We're trapped.
- We might try shouting "fire!"

00:18.129 --> 00:19.850
It's not a crowded theater.

00:19.929 --> 00:22.460
One day I might, yes...

00:23.530 --> 00:27.989
...many years from now,
when I've lost my looks a little.

00:29.530 --> 00:31.070
Do not laugh.

00:31.929 --> 00:33.009
Only another hour.

00:33.729 --> 00:37.170
I mean, of course, a time will come...

00:37.929 --> 00:40.250
...when Torvald is not....

00:40.929 --> 00:42.469
He's not....

00:45.130 --> 00:47.340
- Line!
- "Is not as devoted to me."

00:47.530 --> 00:48.469
Perhaps two.

00:48.729 --> 00:50.340
- What?
- "Is not as devoted."

00:51.130 --> 00:52.710
Right, right, right.

00:52.929 --> 00:56.479
When Torvald is not as devoted to me.

00:58.329 --> 01:00.189
And I thought I knew eternity.

01:02.000 --> 01:08.074
